  <brief_title>Effect of Different Bran-based Dietary Platforms on the Colon Metabolism in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of One Single Dose of Different Bran-based Dietary Platforms on the Colon Metabolism - A Study With (Stable) Isotopes in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
